Megan Fox quietly exchanged marriage vows with her long-time beau, actor Brian Austin Green, in a secret ceremony in Hawaii in mid-June, TMZ.com reported. The couple first met on the set of the TV sitcom 'Hope and Faith.' It's the first marriage for both. Green has an eight-year-old son with actress Vanessa Marcil. Fox and Green best known for his portrayal of David Silver on the TV series 'Beverly Hills, 90210,' are said to be spending their honeymoon at the Four Seasons Hualalai hotel, where the wedding took place.
